666
00:34:05,279 --> 00:34:07,700
[SPEAKER_01] dok se ne riješi ta korupcijska hobotnica.

667
00:34:07,700 --> 00:34:10,000
[SPEAKER_01] Posebno smo usvjereni

668
00:34:10,000 --> 00:34:11,460
[SPEAKER_01] na mali i srednje poduzetnike.

669
00:34:11,460 --> 00:34:12,800
[SPEAKER_01] Recimo, zanimljiv mi je podatak

670
00:34:12,800 --> 00:34:14,599
[SPEAKER_01] da 54% radnih mjesta

671
00:34:14,599 --> 00:34:15,760
[SPEAKER_01] u realnom sektoru

672
00:34:15,760 --> 00:34:18,679
[SPEAKER_01] stvaraju mikro i mali poduzetnici.

673
00:34:18,679 --> 00:34:20,199
[SPEAKER_01] Njih treba pomoći ojačati.

674
00:34:20,199 --> 00:34:21,900
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, dati im poslovnu

675
00:34:21,900 --> 00:34:22,940
[SPEAKER_01] i pravnu sigurnost,

676
00:34:22,940 --> 00:34:24,079
