680
00:34:28,019 --> 00:34:29,219
[SPEAKER_01] i puno drugih stvari.

681
00:34:29,219 --> 00:34:30,840
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, rekao si izborni sustav,

682
00:34:30,840 --> 00:34:31,920
[SPEAKER_00] rekao si sudstvo,

683
00:34:31,920 --> 00:34:33,440
[SPEAKER_00] promjeno gospodarstvo...

684
00:34:33,440 --> 00:34:34,159
[SPEAKER_01] Suverenizam,

685
00:34:34,159 --> 00:34:35,139
