[SPEAKER_01] kao neka puka, značka,

687
00:34:36,420 --> 00:34:37,480
[SPEAKER_01] nego u ovom smislu

688
00:34:37,480 --> 00:34:38,699
[SPEAKER_01] demokratskog deficita

689
00:34:38,699 --> 00:34:41,679
[SPEAKER_01] da mi sami donosimo odluke o sebi,

690
00:34:41,679 --> 00:34:42,940
[SPEAKER_01] a ne da ih prepuštamo

691
00:34:42,940 --> 00:34:45,219
[SPEAKER_01] nekim tijelima izvan nas

692
00:34:45,219 --> 00:34:45,500
[SPEAKER_01] i iznad nas...

693
00:34:45,500 --> 00:34:47,780
[SPEAKER_00] Sigurno ne mogu bolje od nas odlučivati.

694
00:34:47,780 --> 00:34:50,599
[SPEAKER_01] Reforma školstva se pretvorila u lakrdiju.

695
00:34:50,599 --> 00:34:52,139
[SPEAKER_01] To je ključno dugoročno pitanje

696
00:34:52,139 --> 00:34:53,659
