708
00:35:11,840 --> 00:35:12,800
[SPEAKER_01] političkoj trgovini

709
00:35:12,800 --> 00:35:15,079
[SPEAKER_01] dugoročno najvažnije je ministarstvo.

710
00:35:15,079 --> 00:35:16,539
[SPEAKER_01] Da li straničici od 1%

711
00:35:16,539 --> 00:35:18,400
[SPEAKER_01] da vrši svoje eksperimente.

712
00:35:18,400 --> 00:35:18,900
[SPEAKER_00] Sigurno.

713
00:35:18,900 --> 00:35:20,840
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, snažno smo fokusirani

714
00:35:20,840 --> 00:35:24,460
[SPEAKER_01] na školstvo koje treba ojačati.

715
