[SPEAKER_01] prema Bosni i Hercegovini

718
00:35:29,300 --> 00:35:30,179
[SPEAKER_01] i Hrvatima u njoj.

719
00:35:30,179 --> 00:35:31,579
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, maksimalna potpora

720
00:35:31,579 --> 00:35:33,880
[SPEAKER_01] jednakopravnosti Hrvata

721
00:35:33,880 --> 00:35:35,380
[SPEAKER_01] u Bosni i Hercegovini.

722
00:35:35,380 --> 00:35:36,679
[SPEAKER_01] I to treba ići dotle

723
00:35:36,679 --> 00:35:38,360
[SPEAKER_01] da Hrvatska zauzme jasno stajalište.

724
00:35:38,360 --> 00:35:39,260
[SPEAKER_01] Da Bosna i Hercegovina

725
00:35:39,260 --> 00:35:40,559
[SPEAKER_01] neće napraviti ni koraka

726
00:35:40,559 --> 00:35:41,880
[SPEAKER_01] prema evropskim integracijama

727
00:35:41,880 --> 00:35:43,320
[SPEAKER_01] dok se ne riješi izborni zakon.

728
00:35:43,320 --> 00:35:45,820
[SPEAKER_01] Dok se ne vrati na detonska načela

729
00:35:45,820 --> 00:35:47,420
[SPEAKER_01] gdje svaki narod može

730
00:35:47,420 --> 00:35:48,960
[SPEAKER_01] sam sebi birati predstavniki.

731
00:35:48,960 --> 00:35:50,420
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, ne bih ucenjivao

732
00:35:50,420 --> 00:35:51,599
[SPEAKER_01] Bosnu i Hercegovina način

733
