[SPEAKER_01] radi neke bilateralne koriste.

735
00:35:54,880 --> 00:35:56,579
[SPEAKER_01] Govorimo o evropskim načelima.

736
00:35:56,579 --> 00:35:58,480
[SPEAKER_00] A propos Bosne i Hercegovine,

737
00:35:58,480 --> 00:36:00,099
[SPEAKER_00] tebi zamjeraju neki

738
