757
00:36:42,539 --> 00:36:44,340
[SPEAKER_01] autentičnost onome gdje sam kudio.

758
00:36:45,039 --> 00:36:47,219
[SPEAKER_01] U tom trenutku kad je Mostar gorio

759
00:36:47,219 --> 00:36:49,119
[SPEAKER_01] on je otišao dolje i dobio je pijesak

760
00:36:49,119 --> 00:36:50,840
[SPEAKER_01] HDZ ovaca B i H okupljenih

761
00:36:50,840 --> 00:36:52,440
[SPEAKER_01] ispre zapaljene zgrade HDZ.

762
00:36:52,440 --> 00:36:54,159
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, to je bio dobar potez.

763
00:36:54,159 --> 00:36:56,260
[SPEAKER_00] Dobro, ali da li ti misliš da taj jedan dobar potez

764
