768
00:37:04,280 --> 00:37:05,699
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, mi govorimo,

769
00:37:05,699 --> 00:37:08,800
[SPEAKER_01] ocjenjujemo ljude prema njihovim dijelima.

770
00:37:08,800 --> 00:37:10,079
[SPEAKER_00] Dijelima, dobro.

771
00:37:10,079 --> 00:37:12,460
[SPEAKER_01] A onda mi to izlače i kažu

772
00:37:12,460 --> 00:37:14,900
[SPEAKER_01] ovi koji su šutke promatrali majorizaciju

773
00:37:14,900 --> 00:37:16,719
[SPEAKER_01] Hrvata u B i H da sam ja nešto

774
00:37:16,719 --> 00:37:18,719
[SPEAKER_01] kao stajao i promovirao Milanović.

775
00:37:18,719 --> 00:37:20,300
[SPEAKER_00] Pa da, ali ti si onda i rekao da on

776
00:37:20,300 --> 00:37:22,500
[SPEAKER_00] zaštitio tvoju, da si ti osjećao

777
00:37:22,500 --> 00:37:24,539
[SPEAKER_00] da on svojim doloskom štiti i tvoju

778
00:37:24,539 --> 00:37:25,840
[SPEAKER_00] obitelj koja je dolje živjela.

779
00:37:25,840 --> 00:37:28,280
[SPEAKER_01] Naravno, to će vam svako reći dolje

780
00:37:28,280 --> 00:37:31,219
