781
00:37:31,219 --> 00:37:34,360
[SPEAKER_00] Druga stvar o kojoj ti predbacuju je Feral.

782
00:37:34,360 --> 00:37:36,940
[SPEAKER_00] Daj, molim te, objasni nam tu priču.

783
00:37:36,940 --> 00:37:38,840
