[SPEAKER_01] Što dnaći? Onda su pokušali

790
00:37:48,559 --> 00:37:50,840
[SPEAKER_01] iskonstruirati Rasplić kao nekakav konvertit.

791
00:37:50,840 --> 00:37:52,539
[SPEAKER_01] Da sam ja to beže bio neki ljevi čar,

792
00:37:52,539 --> 00:37:53,739
[SPEAKER_01] pa sada je drugačije.

793
00:37:53,739 --> 00:37:55,619
[SPEAKER_01] Pa kaže, pisao za Feral.

794
00:37:55,619 --> 00:37:56,960
[SPEAKER_01] Pa bio suradnik Ferala.

795
00:37:56,960 --> 00:37:58,360
[SPEAKER_01] Pa Robert Bajruši piše

796
00:37:58,360 --> 00:38:00,960
[SPEAKER_01] da sam 90-ih surađivao s Feralom.

797
00:38:00,960 --> 00:38:03,059
[SPEAKER_01] Prava istina da su u Feralu

798
00:38:03,059 --> 00:38:04,800
[SPEAKER_01] objavljena dva teksta,

799
00:38:04,800 --> 00:38:06,219
[SPEAKER_01] jedan 2004. i 2006.

800
00:38:06,219 --> 00:38:09,460
[SPEAKER_01] Jedan intervju s piscem Claudio Magrisem,

801
00:38:09,460 --> 00:38:10,800
[SPEAKER_01] dakle isključivo književnosti,

802
00:38:10,800 --> 00:38:12,280
[SPEAKER_01] koji je vođen u Italijanskom institutu

803
00:38:12,280 --> 00:38:13,440
[SPEAKER_01] za kulturu u Zagrebu,

804
00:38:13,440 --> 00:38:15,300
[SPEAKER_01] koji su onda to spojili da se to objavi

805
00:38:15,300 --> 00:38:17,079
[SPEAKER_01] u pulturnoj rubrici neke novine.

806
00:38:17,079 --> 00:38:19,300
[SPEAKER_01] A drugi je opet vezan za događaj

807
00:38:19,300 --> 00:38:21,639
