808
00:38:21,639 --> 00:38:23,340
[SPEAKER_01] gdje je bio i veliki skup prevoditelja

809
00:38:23,340 --> 00:38:25,099
[SPEAKER_01] Umberta Eka, na kojem sam sudjelovao

810
00:38:25,099 --> 00:38:26,260
[SPEAKER_01] i izlagao jer sam ga prevodio

811
00:38:26,260 --> 00:38:28,079
[SPEAKER_01] i gdje sam imao čast sedam dana

812
00:38:28,079 --> 00:38:29,960
[SPEAKER_01] se družiti s tim velikim piscem

813
00:38:29,960 --> 00:38:31,059
[SPEAKER_01] i intelektualcem.

814
00:38:31,059 --> 00:38:33,139
[SPEAKER_01] I dakle izlazi tekste,

815
00:38:33,139 --> 00:38:34,079
[SPEAKER_01] pročitaću sad cijeli tekst.

816
00:38:34,079 --> 00:38:35,380
[SPEAKER_00] Ali kako je došlo do suradnje?

817
00:38:35,380 --> 00:38:38,159
[SPEAKER_00] To me zanima, oni su tebe zvali,

818
00:38:38,159 --> 00:38:40,800
[SPEAKER_00] oni su angažirali kroz taj kongres

819
00:38:40,800 --> 00:38:41,380
[SPEAKER_00] ili kako je to?

820
00:38:41,380 --> 00:38:43,699
[SPEAKER_01] To je bilo unutar kongresa i sajma knjige u Puli.

821
00:38:43,699 --> 00:38:45,900
[SPEAKER_01] Znate kako novine zovu,

822
00:38:45,900 --> 00:38:48,280
[SPEAKER_01] evo može se nešto napisati i izvijesti.

823
00:38:48,280 --> 00:38:50,920
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle buduća se radi o stvarima vezanim za kulture.

824
00:38:50,920 --> 00:38:51,679
[SPEAKER_01] Evo pročitaću sve.

825
00:38:51,679 --> 00:38:52,599
[SPEAKER_01] Može, pročite.

826
00:38:52,599 --> 00:38:54,579
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, nekoliko usputnih zapisa

827
00:38:54,579 --> 00:38:56,380
[SPEAKER_01] o druženju sa slavnim italijanskim piscem

828
00:38:56,380 --> 00:38:57,159
[SPEAKER_01] Umberto Mekomu,

829
00:38:57,159 --> 00:38:58,719
[SPEAKER_01] okviru skupa ekovih prevoditelja

830
00:38:58,719 --> 00:38:59,800
[SPEAKER_01] održanog u Puli.

831
00:38:59,800 --> 00:39:01,039
[SPEAKER_01] Čulte uhu.

832
00:39:01,039 --> 00:39:03,340
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, ovo je kompletno ljevičarenje

833
00:39:03,340 --> 00:39:06,079
