837
00:39:11,880 --> 00:39:13,820
[SPEAKER_01] prolazio je pored golf igrališta,

838
00:39:13,820 --> 00:39:15,300
[SPEAKER_01] na kojem je skupina igrača,

839
00:39:15,300 --> 00:39:16,980
[SPEAKER_01] pripadnika naše dične elite,

840
00:39:16,980 --> 00:39:18,699
[SPEAKER_01] važno obilazila oko rupice.

841
00:39:18,699 --> 00:39:21,739
[SPEAKER_01] Eko je nakratko izvadio cigaru iz usta

842
00:39:21,739 --> 00:39:23,480
[SPEAKER_01] i dikcijom profesora koji izriče

843
00:39:23,480 --> 00:39:24,800
